title: Aurora Borealis
description: A stunning display of the Northern Lights, featuring vibrant green and blue hues swirling across the night sky, set against a dark landscape with distant hills.

title: Serene Beach at Sunset
description: A tranquil beach scene during sunset, featuring gentle waves lapping at the shore. In the background, a rugged coastline rises with a mountain silhouette against a colorful sky, transitioning from orange to purple hues as the sun sets.

title: Volcanic Eruption
description: A dramatic scene of a volcanic eruption, showcasing molten lava flowing down the side of a dark, rocky surface. The sky is clear, with a hint of smoke rising from the volcano's peak, and the bright orange and red hues of the lava contrast against the darker landscape.

title: Graph Representation
description: A simple graph with a vertical axis (y-axis) and a horizontal axis (x-axis). The y-axis is labeled with a scale, while the x-axis is a straight line without any markings. The graph appears to be empty, indicating no data points or trends are plotted.

title: Simple Geometric Design
description: A minimalist black background with a thin white line forming a rectangle at the top and a vertical line on the left side.

title: Scenic Mountain Lake
description: A breathtaking view of a serene lake surrounded by lush green forests and majestic mountains. The clear blue water reflects the sky, and the landscape is dotted with trees and a small village near the shore.
